---
layout: default
---
%header
  .container
    %h1.text-center Experienced Business Design and Development.
.hero.primary-bg
  .text-center
    %h1{style: "font-size:64px;"}
      MIKE & DAN
    %h3{style: "color:white;"}
      Fast Fixes to Full Features.
    %a{href:"#contact", class: 'btn cta-btn', style: 'margin-top:25px;'}
      Get Started
      %i.fa.fa-chevron-down
.container
  .row
    .col-sm-4
      .content-box
        .icon
          %span.fa-stack.fa-2x
            %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            %i.fa.fa-paint-brush.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.text-center
          Design
        %p
          The first, and most important step, to a succesful project is to build your brand and identity. We’ll help you get from IDEA to MOCKUP, making sure you website or mobile app is an organic extension of your business. Each project starts with a WIREFRAME so that you don’t waste time or money on unwanted development.
    .col-sm-4
      .content-box
        .icon
          %span.fa-stack.fa-2x
            %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            %i.fa.fa-code.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.text-center
          Develop
        %p
          Our process includes rapid prototyping with HTML5, CSS3, and JAVASCRIPT. We use popular frameworks like RAILS, BOOTSTRAP, and REACTJS so that you’re never left stranded with custom, costly code. From MVP to full-featured, we’ll make sure your business can grow into the future, and even be ready for a future developer.
    .col-sm-4
      .content-box
        .icon
          %span.fa-stack.fa-2x
            %i.fa.fa-circle.fa-stack-2x
            %i.fa.fa-line-chart.fa-stack-1x.fa-inverse
        %h4.text-center
          Optimize
        %p
          Releasing your website is just the first step to building a successful company. Our greatest value is helping you identify how you can make the most of your business through A/B TESTING, CRM AUTOMATION, and LEAD GENERATION. Building a website isn’t just about delivering content, it’s about ENGAGING your customers.
#contact.primary-bg
  .container{style: 'margin-top:50px'}
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
        .pre-well
          %h2
            Let's work together...
          %h5
            You can email us directly, chat us on slack, or preferably fill out the form.
        %form#contact-form{action: "//formspree.io/mglobel@gmail.com", method: "POST"}
          .well
            %h4 Your Contact Info
            .row
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Name
                  %input.form-control{name: "name", type: "text"}
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Email
                  %input.form-control{name: "_replyto", type: "email"}
            .row
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Phone
                  %input.form-control{name: "phone", type: "tel"}
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label.control-label Company
                  %input.form-control{name: "business", type: "text"}
          .well
            %h4 Project Info
            .row
              .col-xs-12
                %label What type of services are you looking for? Check all that apply
                .form-group{id: "projectType"}
                  .row
                    .col-sm-6
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Web Design"}
                            Web Design / Redesign
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Web Development"}
                            Web Development / Coding
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Marketing"}
                            Marketing / SEO
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Email Automation"}
                            Email Automation
                    .col-sm-6
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "CRM Implementation"}
                            CRM Implementation
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "eCommerce"}
                            eCommerce
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Search Results"}
                            Search Result / Filters
                      .checkbox
                        %label
                          %input{type: "checkbox", name: "project_type[]", value: "Client Management"}
                            Client Management
            .row
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label Project Budget
                  %select.form-control{name: "project_budjet"}
                    %option Less than $2000
                    %option $2000 - $3000
                    %option $3000 - $5000
                    %option Over $5000
              .col-sm-6
                .form-group
                  %label Project Timeline
                  %select.form-control{name: "project_timeline"}
                    %option As soon as possible
                    %option Within 2 weeks
                    %option Within a month
                    %option Undetermined
            .form-group
              %label.control-label Project Details
              %textarea.form-control{name: "projectDetails", rows: "3"}
            %input.btn.btn-success.btn-lg{type: "submit", value: "Submit"}
        :javascript
